body: "Validation evidence: pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift --check-files --scan-mode tracked-all returned ok=false with warnings: validate_resolution_missing_fields:18, validate_files_missing_linked_paths:3, validate_history_drift_hash_mismatches:3. These appear historical/pre-existing and were not silently mass-edited because each closed item needs item-specific resolution context."
